{"tid":1542801,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【反送中】其實我有呢個idea好耐，身邊人話我太前衛","createTime":"2019-09-05T03:31:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T05:34:17.000Z","uid":88966,"like":14,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"d35959c21e5aaadc3560466128c453a889f2fc9d","tid":1542801,"uid":88966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T03:31:52.000Z","msg":"由6月9到6月12，見證住身邊做咗成世豬嘅朋友，俾大家嘅文宣感染，開始慢慢對社會關心。<br />\n<br />\n再到後期721、811，黑白對錯已經好明顯，仲唔醒個啲，根本再多文宣、連儂牆、airdrop、新聞，佢地都係繼續扮中立嘅扮中立，顛倒是非嘅顛倒是非。<br />\n<br />\n好似入咗個胡同到，傷者同被捕人數不停增加，對家就絲毫無損。<br />\n<br />\n講返個idea。<br />\n呢個post開係創意台係有原因嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為個idea真係好怪，但如果呢個幫到個運動向前，等大家唔好再受傷同輕生，我會好開心。<br />\n<br />\n曾經有人話過，如果屋企人藍，要俾佢更藍，甚至染紅自己。<br />\n如果呢場運動都可以呢？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">黃同藍</span> <br />\n即使對家都有損傷 但我地何嘗唔係傷亡慘重？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">紅</span>同藍</span><br />\n1）拎晒國旗唱國歌出嚟遊行，口號改一改：公安全面取替警察，唔要香港軍政府、光復香港，我愛祖國，之類。<br />\n<br />\n2）連儂牆清一色愛國宣言，反支持信用評級制度，大推送中，以紅色恐怖破你嘅白色恐怖。<br />\n<br />\n3）黑色bye bye轉用紅色，當大家玩得純熟，仲可以開始加入批鬥元素。<br />\n<br />\n4）機場、佔路等，愛國如同攞咗免死金牌。<br />\n<br />\n即使對家明知都係同一班人，但係佢地可以做嘅文宣會少咗，顛倒黑白嘅人，今次黑同白都係我地，點講都幫咗我地。<br />\n<br />\n警察拉人都受到制肘，當愛國標語同國旗都出埋，官媒可以影嘅角度少咗，但獨立媒體可以照影住，「向愛國人士射催淚彈？」好似唔係咁易。<br />\n<br />\n班中立木咀，通常都係最怕攬炒個班。而家同佢地理論係晒鳩氣，因為有成班人攞埋條命幫佢爭取，所以佢先有心機屌你用錯方法。你越叫佢地唔好，佢地偏要做，今次我地大大力攬炒，得返佢地孤軍作戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，佢地先會真正覺醒。<br />\n<br />\n重點係，咁樣絕對可以減少受傷、俾狗姦、同手足輕生嘅機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實我一直都係CD mon<br />\n對唔住1999<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e931f2a85537caf9b6002c7ee5fc8d21db1f281","tid":1542801,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T03:32:03.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M5EAUpQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM5EAUpQ.jpg&h=30bf1600&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UUE1PYa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUUE1PYa.jpg&h=d8331036&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1sNZBDb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1sNZBDb.jpg&h=ace5c24e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8KM7Lwx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8KM7Lwx.jpg&h=5719ebc4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SoyFk4T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSoyFk4T.jpg&h=2bffae59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SsV05wz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSsV05wz.jpg&h=d54e941c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EUH604U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEUH604U.jpg&h=74590733&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bd039430e77ac1395f0a2954469760e122df567f","tid":1542801,"uid":58140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T03:33:32.000Z","msg":"暗黑兵法嚟㗎喎ching"},{"pid":"81c79a48829b668870212905648ee9b464f6ffea","tid":1542801,"uid":262674,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T03:33:36.000Z","msg":"唔同意<br />\n<br />\n完"},{"pid":"dec23d6aba83a5a9ee40154253d1798078bc861e","tid":1542801,"uid":47905,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T03:34:03.000Z","msg":"